The chain of pain:

Content is in AC3/DTS because Blu-ray mandates it
Browsers can't play it because Dolby charges too much
You can't transcode server-side because Debrid IP-locks links
You can't decode client-side because WebAssembly kills mobile
You can't go native because Apple charges $99
